-- Steny Hoyer to Run for House Democratic Whip, Setting Up Race With Clyburn
-- B y   J a m e s   R o w l e y
-- 2010-11-08T22:12:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-08/steny-hoyer-to-run-for-house-democratic-whip-setting-up-race-with-clyburn.html
Steny Hoyer of Maryland said he will
run for the House Democrats’ second-ranking leadership job,
setting up a race for minority whip against James Clyburn of
South Carolina.  Hoyer, the current majority leader, said in a statement
today he has received “support from across the breadth of our
caucus” to remain on the leadership team. The Democrats will
become the minority party in January.  To contact the reporter on this story:
James Rowley in Washington at 
 jarowley@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Laurie Asseo at 
 lasseo1@bloomberg.net  